name: Slide Puzzler
description:
A circular slide puzzle generator, similar to the Figsaw puzzle generator, but now with ALL CIRCLES.

Paste in your favorite image and watch as it is spliced and rotated across many different angles.

Head over to the First Puzzle page inside the document for a multi-player experience that works far better than doing this puzzle alone! Video chatting required. You can still do this puzzle alone too, but much more fun with friends!
